snippet.title: Sol 0 Greenlight Trailer
snippet.description:
Vote for Sol 0 on Steam Greenlight!

http://www.solzerogame.com
Demo (Free) / Purchase ($3.99): http://www.solzerogame.com/store.php

Can you survive on Mars? Sol 0 is a Mars colonization city building game. Manage power, water, food, oxygen, and other resources while surviving the harsh Martian climate.

Music credit:
Tempting Secrets, Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
